0federal%20court%20last%20Friday%2C%20shows%20Altman%20reaching%20out%20to%20Zilis%20on%20February%209%2C%202023%2C%20seeking%20advice%20on%20whether%20to%20publicly%20praise%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBTW%2C%20good%20idea%20for%20me%20to%20tweet%20something%20nice%20about%20Elon%3F%20Have%20been%20meaning%20to%20do%20this%20after%20he%20DMd%20about%20not%20being%20in%20the%20photo%20from%20the%20first%20day%20of%20OpenAI.%20Just%20about%20how%20much%20I%20and%20others%20look%20up%20to%20him%2C%20how%20critical%20his%20early%20contributions%20to%20OpenAI%20are%2C%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote%2C%20according%20to%20the%20document.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20week%20later%2C%20Altman%20seemed%20to%20enact%20this%2C%20posting%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3Bsociety%20underestimates%20how%20much%20it%20owes%20elon%20for%20raising%20the%20collective%20ambition%20level%20at%20a%20time%20when%20optimism%20for%20the%20future%20was%20receding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9fdb094-d0b2-4c94-8487-c7fcbced76cc%5C%22%3EA%20glimpse%20behind%20the%20message%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20sheds%20light%20on%20how%20Altman%20tried%20to%20repair%20his%20relationship%20with%20Musk%2C%20who%20had%20grown%20increasingly%20critical%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findustries-openai-is-disrupting-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20the%20two%20helped%20launch%20in%202015%20with%20a%20shared%20mission%20to%20develop%20artificial%20intelligence%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20suggests%20that%20Altman%20sought%20to%20smooth%20things%20over%20by%20publicly%20acknowledging%20Musk's%20early%20role%20in%20the%20company.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZilis%2C%20who%20reportedly%20has%20four%20children%20with%20Musk%2C%20has%20long%20served%20as%20one%20of%20Musk's%20most%20trusted%20lieutenants%2C%20working%20as%20director%20of%20operations%20and%20special%20projects%20at%20Neuralink.%20Her%20communications%20were%20produced%20as%20evidence%20by%20her%20legal%20team%20and%20entered%20as%20Exhibit%2035%20in%20the%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20message%20was%20among%20dozens%20of%20emails%2C%20depositions%2C%20and%20text%20threads%20submitted%20by%20Musk's%20lawyers%20to%20support%20his%20argument%20that%20OpenAI%20abandoned%20its%20founding%20mission%20of%20developing%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9bb1b78-c1ae-42d9-876f-0ff6089ba4fa%5C%22%3EOld%20scars%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECourt%20documents%20show%20that%20years%20before%20Altman's%20conciliatory%20post%20on%20X%2C%20he%20and%20Musk%20had%20already%20clashed%20over%20OpenAI's%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmails%20from%20February%202016%2C%20shared%20in%20the%20court%20documents%2C%20suggest%20that%20Musk%20was%20deeply%20involved%20in%20the%20company's%20operations%20%E2%80%94%20messaging%20cofounders%20about%20meeting%20regularly%20and%20warning%20that%20competitors%20were%20%26quot%3Bplaying%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20and%20we%20are%20playing%20the%20Puppy%20Bowl.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20by%20September%202017%2C%20frustration%20had%20boiled%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20exchange%20filed%20as%20Exhibit%2041%2C%20Musk%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BGuys%2C%20I've%20had%20enough.%20This%20is%20the%20final%20straw.%20Either%20go%20do%20something%20on%20your%20own%20or%20continue%20with%20OpenAI%20as%20a%20nonprofit.%20I%20will%20no%20longer%20fund%20OpenAI%20until%20you%20have%20made%20a%20firm%20commitment%20to%20stay%20or%20I'm%20just%20being%20a%20fool%20who%20is%20essentially%20providing%20free%20funding%20for%20you%20to%20create%20a%20startup.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20responded%20the%20next%20day%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20remain%20enthusiastic%20about%20the%20non-profit%20structure!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20back-and-forth%20%E2%80%94%20Altman%20placating%2C%20Musk%20erupting%20%E2%80%94%20would%20become%20a%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20years%20later%2C%20his%20text%20to%20Zilis%20reads%20almost%20like%20a%20reprise%20of%20those%20earlier%20emails%3A%20another%20private%20effort%20to%20soothe%20a%20public%20feud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228df211be-ecd6-4f76-9a37-db1a4959ab4e%5C%22%3EFrom%20private%20message%20to%20public%20praise%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAltman's%20February%2013%20post%20on%20X%20was%20widely%20interpreted%20as%20an%20olive%20branch%20toward%20Musk%2C%20who%20by%20then%20had%20begun%20publicly%20criticizing%20OpenAI's%20commercial%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20newly%20revealed%20message%20suggests%20that%20the%20post%20was%20less%20spontaneous%20than%20it%20appeared%20%E2%80%94%20a%20calculated%20gesture%20that%20was%20shaped%20behind%20the%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Musk%20v.%20Altman%20filings%20trace%20years%20of%20strained%20communication%20between%20the%20two%20founders.%20Musk%20resigned%20from%20OpenAI's%20board%20in%202018%2C%20five%20years%20later%20launching%20xAI%2C%20his%20own%20AI%20company%2C%20and%20repeatedly%20accusing%20OpenAI%20of%20betraying%20its%20nonprofit%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Altman%2C%20Zilis%2C%20nor%20lawyers%20for%20Musk%20immediately%20responded%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20message.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%2C%20filed%20in%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20California%2C%20is%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20filings%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20from%20the%20Zilis%20message%20%E2%80%94%20offer%20a%20rare%20glimpse%20into%20how%20two%20of%20Silicon%20Valley's%20most%20influential%20figures%20navigated%2C%20and%20at%20times%20massaged%2C%20their%20uneasy%20relationship%20in%20the%20high-stakes%20world%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-asked-elon-musk-confidante-abo