0could%20face%20losses%20between%20%245%2C800%20and%20around%20%2410%2C000.%20It%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20disaster%20for%20working-class%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20punishing%20IDR%20beneficiaries%20with%20massive%20tax%20bills%2C%20the%20federal%20government%20undermines%20the%20very%20purpose%20of%20the%20IDR%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawmakers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmakers%20outlined%20several%20legal%20authorities%20they%20said%20the%20administration%20could%20use%20to%20prevent%20new%20tax%20bills%20on%20student-debt%20relief.%20One%20authority%20the%20lawmakers%20referenced%20is%20a%20general%20welfare%20exclusion%3B%20they%20said%20that%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%2C%20by%20nature%2C%20suggest%20a%20borrower's%20demonstrated%20need%20since%20payments%20are%20based%20on%20income%2C%20and%20loan%20forgiveness%20would%20promote%20the%20borrower's%20general%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20letter%20follows%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-back-on-ibr-borrowers-debt-relief-processing-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eresumption%20of%20student-loan%20forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20borrowers%20on%20income-based%20repayment%20plans.%20In%20early%20October%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20resumed%20processing%20relief%20for%20borrowers%20who%20reached%20the%20required%20number%20of%20payments%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-paused-ibr-trump-halts-borrower-debt-relief-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eafter%20pausing%20the%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20in%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20discharge%20notices%20that%20borrowers%20received%20said%20that%20the%20date%20they%20completed%20their%20qualifying%20payments%20would%20be%20considered%20the%20effective%20date%20of%20the%20relief.%20So%2C%20if%20a%20bo