20expanded%20the%20potential%20content%20to%20include%20pets%20and%20even%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20viral%20app%2C%20which%20at%20times%20led%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20for%20free%20apps%2C%20is%20built%20on%20OpenAI's%20Sora-2%20video%20generation%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20has%20created%20leaderboards%20for%20users%20who%20generate%20the%20most%20popular%20videos%20or%20whose%20linkness%20is%20featured%20the%20most%2C%20underlining%20how%20the%20AI%20company%20is%20building%20out%20the%20app%20as%20an%20entry%20into%20the%20social%20media%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20was%20already%20trying%20to%20fend%20off%20TikTok%20through%20Instagram's%20Reels%20feature.%20The%20future%20of%20TikTok%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20Chinese-based%20ByteDance%2C%20in%20the%20US%20remains%20uncertain.%20In%20September%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20that%20would%20transfer%20control%20of%20the%20app%20and%20its%20prized%20algorithm%20to%20Americans.%20As%20of%20early%20November%2C%20the%20deal%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20finalized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHealthcare%3Cp%3EHealthcare%20remains%20a%20core%20focus%20of%20OpenAI's%20future%20aspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20exploring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-killed-personal-health-record-openai-chatgpt-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20its%20own%20consumer%20health%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Business%20Insider%20first%20reported%20in%20November.%20Sources%20close%20to%20the%20company%20said%20the%20AI%20company%20is%20weighing%20various%20opportunities%2C%20including%20creating%20a%20personal%20health%20assistant%20or%20a%20health%20data%20aggregator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-taps-doximity-cofounder-to-lead-its-next-healthcare-push-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20tapped%20Nate%20Gross%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20lead%20its%20health%20strategy.%20Gross%20was%20the%20cofounder%20and%20former%20chief%20strategy%20officer%20at%20Doximity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20are%20increasingly%20entering%20the%20healthcare%20space.%20Amazon%20made%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20splashes%20in%202022%20with%20the%20acquisition%20of%20OneMedical%2C%20a%20primary%20care%20startup%2C%20for%20%243.9%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20outlining%20OpenAI's%20future%2C%20Altman%20said%20that%20one%20of%20the%20initial%20focuses%20of%20the%20OpenAI%20foundation%2C%20which%20is%20now%20separate%20from%20the%20company%2C%20will%20be%20using%20AI%20to%20cure%20diseases.%20The%20foundation%20pledged%20%2425%20billion%20to%20that%20endeavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPayments%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20increasingly%20adding%20e-commerce%20functions%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20OpenAI%20announced%20a%20partnership%20with%20PayPal%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20use%20the%20payment%20platform%20to%20make%20purchases%20in%20ChatGPT%20starting%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20may%20have%20grander%20plans%20for%20the%20financial%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20October%2C%20Roi%2C%20an%20investment%20startup%2C%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20been%20acquired%20by%20OpenAI%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20sum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20Roi%203%20years%20ago%20to%20make%20investing%20accessible%20to%20everyone%20by%20building%20the%20most%20personalized%20financial%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Roi%20CEO%20Sujith%20Vishwajith%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20announcing%20the%20deal.%20%26quot%3BAlong%20the%20way%20we%20realized%20personalization%20isn't%20just%20the%20future%20of%20finance.%20It's%20the%20future%20of%20software.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EConsumer%20hardware%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20(left)%20and%20Jony%20Ive%20(right)%20chat%20on%20stake%20at%20OpenAI's%20DevDay%20conference%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690e6f237f37aa653f55ac17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Altman%20(left)%20and%20Jony%20Ive%20(right)%20chat%20on%20stake%20at%20OpenAI's%20DevDay%20conference%3Cp%3EAlistair%20Barr%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer%20devices%20might%20remain%20the%20murkiest%20part%20of%20OpenAI's%20future%20aspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20OpenAI%20announced%20its%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-jony-ive-io-startup-apple-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%246.5%20billion%20acquisition%20of%20io%20Products%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20company%20cofounder%20by%20legendary%20iPhone%20designer%20Jony%20Ive.%20OpenAI%20also%20revealed%20that%20Altman%20and%20Ive%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bquietly%26quot%3B%20collaborating%20since%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Ive%20told%20Altman%20during%20a%20fireside%20chat%20at%20OpenAI's%20DevDay%20conference%20that%20he%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjony-ive-ideas-openai-family-ai-devices-sam-altman-design-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E15%20to%2020%20ideas%20for%20OpenAI%20devices.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20challenge%20is%20to%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20Ive%20told%20Altman%20onstage.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20easy%20if%20you%20knew%20there%20are%20three%20good%20ones.%20It's%20just%20not%20like%20that.%20We're%20designing%20a%20family%20of%20products.%20And%20we're%20trying%20to%20make%20sure%20we're%20judicious%20and%20thoughtful%20in%20what%20we%20focus%20on%20and%20to%20then%20not%20be%20distracted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChipmaking%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20has%20a%20ceaseless%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpus-capacity-demand-advancements-altman-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eappetite%20for%20more%20compute.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Altman%20outlined%20the%20%241.4%20trillion%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20spend%20in%20the%20years%20ahead%20for%20roughly%2030%20gigawatts%20of%20data%20center%20capacity.%20Aspirationally%2C%20Altman%20said%20OpenAI%20is%20considering%20plans%20that%20would%20potentially%20allow%20it%20to%20create%201%20gigawatt%20of%20computing%20power%20a%20week%20by%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20needs%20advanced%20chips%20to%20fulfill%20these%20needs.%20In%20September%2C%20OpenAI%20announced%20a%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whereby%20Nvidia%20would%20invest%20up%20to%20%24100%20billion%20in%20OpenAI%2C%20as%20each%20of%20gigawatt%20of%20at%20least%2010%20gigawatts%20of%20data%20center%20capacity%20is%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20month%20later%2C%20OpenAI%20announced%20that%20it%20is%20working%20with%20Broadcom%2C%20another%20chipmaker%2C%20to%20build%20its%20own%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20do%20your%20own%20chips%2C%20you%20control%20your%20destiny%2C%26quot%3B%20Broadcom%20CEO%20Hock%20Tan%20said%20on%20a%20podcast%20announcing%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findustries-openai-is-disrupting-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762772941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690e2a8821c3f142ebfc52b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findustries-openai-is-disrupting-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sam%20Altman%20is%20increasingly%20leading%20OpenAI%20into%20spaces%20beyond%20AI%20research%2C%20disrupting%20industries%20like%20search%2C%20social%2