0and%20who%20love%20you%2C%20and%20then%20ask%20them%20who%20else%20they'd%20recommend%2C%26quot%3B%20Cleavinger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c838d70c-b4fe-4abd-bdab-39cd4bd69fb8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20make%20it%20awkward%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20reaching%20out%20to%20someone%20you%20know%2C%20set%20something%20up%20by%20saying%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI'd%20love%20to%20just%20catch%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViewing%20the%20conversation%20this%20way%2C%20Cleavinger%20said%2C%20can%20also%20prevent%20you%20from%20feeling%20like%20you%20need%20to%20slip%20in%20a%20ham-handed%20job%20ask%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20call.%20There's%20also%20no%20need%20to%20request%20that%20the%20person%20let%20you%20know%20if%20they%20hear%20anything%20about%20a%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20have%20a%20positive%20view%20of%20you%20after%20the%20conversation%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20think%20of%20you%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECleavinger%20said%20that%20instead%20of%20asking%20for%20a%20job%2C%20inquire%20about%20other%20people%20you%20should%20connect%20with%20who%20might%20be%20willing%20to%20have%20similar%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20expanding%20the%20size%20of%20your%20listening%20audience%2C%20because%20recency%20is%20going%20to%20remind%20them%20that%20you're%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStein%2C%20who%20previously%20worked%20in%20Big%20Tech%20at%20firms%20including%20Facebook%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Salesforce%2C%20said%20he%20recently%20followed%20his%20own%20guidance%20on%20networking%20by%20meeting%20with%20a%20high-level%20executive%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStein%20said%20conversations%20like%20these%20are%20a%20chance%20to%20build%20a%20genuine%20connection.%20The%20exec%20ended%20up%20giving%20him%20some%20%26quot%3Bfantastic%20advice%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20guidance%20on%20how%20Stein%20could%20use%