500%20equal-weighted%20index%20may%20provide%20a%20hedge%20against%20tech-driven%20stock%20declines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20concentration%20in%20tech%20stocks%20has%20led%20to%20recent%20underperformance%20in%20the%20cap-weighted%20index.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELower%20valuations%20and%20broadening%20growth%20could%20fuel%20outperformance%20for%20the%20equal-weighted%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20equal-weighted%20index%2C%20to%20be%20frank%2C%20has%20been%20a%20rather%20lackluster%20way%20to%20own%20the%20market%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20last%20half-decade%2C%20it's%20up%2063%25%20while%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-more-concentrated-than-ever-ai-tech-morningstar-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etech-concentrated%20cap-weighted%20index%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%20hear%20about%20more%20often%20is%20up%2093%25.%20In%20the%20last%2012%20months%2C%20the%20equal-weighted%20index%20has%20risen%20just%202%25%20while%20the%20cap-weighted%20index%20is%20up%2012%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20underperformance%20has%20a%20simple%20explanation.%20Tech%20and%20tech-adjacent%20stocks%20have%20dominated%20the%20market%2C%20and%20since%20they're%20the%20largest%20by%20market%20capitalization%2C%20they%20contribute%20more%20to%20the%20returns%20of%20the%20cap-weighted%20index.%20The%20equal-weighted%20index%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20weights%20all%20of%20its%20constituents%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-analysis-sp500-technical-level-tech-ai-stocks-selloff-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etech%20sector%20and%20mega-cap%20stocks%20selling%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20past%20week%2C%20it%20could%20finally%20be%20the%20equal-weighted%20index's%20time%20to%20shine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20this%20week%20balked%20at%20lofty%20tech%20stock%20valuations%20and%20spending%20on%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Technology%20Select%20Sector%20SPDR%20Fund%20(XLK)%20is%20down%205.6%25%20since%20November%203.%20The%20underperformance%20in%20tech%20has%20dragged%20down%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20cap-weighted%20index%20by%202.7%25%20in%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20cap-weighted%20index%20has%20fallen%20just%200.4%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20investors'%20retreat%20from%20the%20tech%20sector%20continues%2C%20the%20equal-weighted%20index%20could%20be%20an%20effective%20way%20to%20hedge%20downside%20risk%20in%20the%20cap-weighted%20strategy%2C%20as%20its%20performance%20hinges%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20a%20select%20few%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20any%20point%20in%20time%20you%20could%20have%20a%20very%20big%20drawdown%20in%20these%20stocks%2C%20and%20that%20would%20not%20be%20unusual%20because%20these%20are%20volatile%20stocks%2C%26quot%3B%20Hank%20Smith%2C%20the%20director%20%26amp%3B%20head%20of%20investment%20strategy%20at%20The%20Haverford%20Trust%20Company%2C%20said%20about%20AI-focused%20mega-cap%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20investors%20understand%20the%20risk%20they're%20taking%20buying%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%20when%20you%20consider%2010%20names%20in%20a%20500%20stock%20index%20represent%2040%25%20plus%20of%20the%20index%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThree%20names%20represent%2025%20give%20or%20take%25%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%3A%20Nvidia%2C%20Microsoft%20and%20Apple.%20That%20is%20extraordinary%20concentration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20protection%20from%20over-concentration%2C%20there%20are%20reasons%20to%20believe%20the%20equal-weighted%20index%20could%20outperform%20the%20cap-weighted%20index%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20while%20the%20equal-weighted%20index's%20recent%20performance%20has%20been%20relatively%20poor%2C%20it%20has%20actually%20outpaced%20the%20cap-weighted%20index%20by%201.05%25%20on%20an%20average%20annual%20basis%20from%201989-2023%2C%20according%20to%20Invesco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20also%20said%20that%20the%20equal-weighted%20index's%20low%20valuations%20also%20make%20it%20an%20attractive%20buy.%20Its%2012-month%20forward%20PE%20ratio%20is%20around%2022%2C%20while%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20cap-weighted%20index's%20is%20around%2030.%20Invesco%20pointed%20out%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20relative%20valuations%20between%20the%20two%20indexes%20are%20about%20as%20far%20apart%20as%20they%20have%20been%20in%20the%20last%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Smith%20argues%20that%20broadening%20economic%20growth%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20been%20largely%20supported%20by%20AI%20capital%20expenditures%20%E2%80%94%20would%20also%20benefit%20the%20equal-weighted%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20correct%20on%20our%20economic%20outlook%2C%20stronger%20growth%20would%20support%20that%20broadening%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20would%20suggest%20that%20maybe%20over%20the%20next%206%20to%209%20months%2C%20you%20might%20see%20better%20relative%20performance%20from%20the%20equal-weighted%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-sp500-tech-sell-off-equal-weight-index-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762770601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690e557821c3f142ebfc596c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-sp500-tech-sell-off-equal-weight-index-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20tech%20sector%20and%20mega-cap%20stocks%20selling%20off%2C%20it%20could%20finally%20be%20the%20equal-weighted%20index's%20time%20to%20shine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F