g%20together%20and%20building%20viral%20apps%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20Christmas%20light%20installation%20app%20that%20made%20%2460%2C000%20in%20revenue%2C%20Dhawan%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20still%20in%20business%20together%2C%20now%20running%20Turbo%20AI%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-notetaker-work-meetings-tech-save-time-boost-efficiency-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enotetaking%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20grown%20from%201%20million%20to%205.7%20million%20users%20in%20the%20past%20six%20months.%20The%20company%20says%20the%20app%20is%20adding%20about%2020%2C000%20new%20users%20each%20day%20and%20is%20on%20track%20to%20earn%20eight-figures%20in%20annual%20recurring%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229b5edf0-4618-4fff-a7ce-c7b0734e8061%5C%22%3EThey%20couldn't%20find%20an%20AI%20tool%20for%20students%2C%20so%20they%20built%20one.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20for%20Turbo%20came%20after%20the%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvaluable-college-majors-degrees-salary-unemployment-engineering-science-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estarted%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%20Arora%20was%20attending%20Northwestern%2C%20and%20Dhawan%20was%20at%20Duke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20problem%20where%20I%20could%20never%20take%20notes%20and%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20teacher%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhawan%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20AI%20was%20starting%20to%20boom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Young%20Geniuses%20series%20spotlights%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20founders%2C%20innovators%2C%20and%20thinkers%20working%20to%20reshape%20industries%20and%20solve%20global%20challenges.%20See%20more%20stories%20from%20the%20series%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-geniuses-child-prodigies-inventing-founding-science-business-tech-solutions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20reach%20out%20to%20editor%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjessica-orwig%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Jess%20Orwig%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhawan%20and%20Arora%20decided%20to%20build%20and%20test%20a%20tool%20that%20leveraged%20AI%20to%20record%20lectures%20and%20generate%20notes%2C%20flashcards%2C%20and%20quizzes%20to%20enhance%20the%20learning%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20mistake%20Turbo%20as%20a%20shortcut%20for%20slackers%2C%20however.%20Dhawan%20and%20Arora%20both%20have%20serious%20academic%20credentials.%20Dhawan%20was%20the%20salutatorian%20of%20his%20high%20school%2C%20took%2021%20AP%20classes%2C%20and%20earned%20a%20perfect%20score%20on%20the%20ACT%2C%20while%20Arora%20took%2016%20AP%20courses%20and%20earned%20a%201560%20on%20the%20SAT%2C%20which%20they've%20noted%20on%20their%20LinkedIn%20profiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20channeling%20their%20own%20experience%20as%20top%20students%20to%20develop%20Turbo's%20internal%20benchmarking%20system%2C%20which%20tests%20different%20combinations%20of%20inputs%20and%20outputs%20to%20pinpoint%20the%20information%20that%20matters%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20notetaking%20apps%20have%20become%20a%20hot%20category%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20Granola%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-notetaking-app-granola-changed-meeting-summary-highlights-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20notetaking%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20launched%20in%202024%2C%20announced%20a%20%2443%20million%20Series%20B%20round%20in%20May.%20Read%20AI%2C%20an%20AI%20assistant%20founded%20in%202021%20that%20creates%20AI-generated%20summaries%2C%20transcriptions%2C%20and%20video%20highlights%20of%20meetings%2C%20announced%20a%20%2450%20million%20Series%20B%20funding%20round%20in%20October%202024.%20Even%20established%20players%20in%20the%20productivity%20market%20like%20Zoom%20and%20Notion%20have%20launched%20AI%20notetaking%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Dhawan%20and%20Arora%20first%20launched%20Turbo%20last%20year%2C%20they%20said%20there%20wasn't%20much%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20actually%20nothing%20for%20students%20on%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20also%20part%20of%20a%20reason%20for%20our%20success%20%E2%80%94%20we've%20been%20doing%20it%20for%20longer%20than%20the%20other%20competitors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20launch%20was%20scrappy.%20They%20made%20rounds%20on%20their%20respective%20campuses%2C%20gave%20out%20cookies%2C%20and%20put%20up%20posters%20inside%20bathroom%20stalls%2C%20Arora%20said.%20Then%20they%20took%20to%20social%20media.%20%26quot%3BI%20posted%20like%2040%2C%2050%20TikToks%2C%20and%20then%20the%2040th%20or%2050th%20one%20went%20mega%20viral.%20It%20got%20like%2020%20million%20views%2C%26quot%3B%20Arora%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20now%20have%20users%20at%20colleges%20across%20the%20country%2C%20including%20Harvard%20and%20MIT.%20They%20said%20they%20even%20have%20customers%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-partners-advice-new-managing-directors-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20few%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-employee-numbers-dropped-5000-consulting-slowdown-overhiring-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eemployees%20at%20McKinsey%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They've%20both%20now%20dropped%20out%20of%20college%20and%20have%20a%20full-time%20team%20of%2015%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20makes%20money%20through%20subscriptions%20%E2%80%94%20%2420%20a%20month%20or%20%24120%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20and%20has%20been%20bootstrapped%20since%20launch.%20It%20raised%20a%20little%20over%20%24750%2C000%20from%20inbound%20investor%20interest.%20The%20founde